        "content": "0.4 - COLOR DEFINITION SCHEMES"
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "Use this panel to set background and character colors on SPF/PC"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "menus and panels.  The colors you select are used on all menus"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "and panels."
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "SPF/PC color schemes enable users to select entire collections"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "of relatively appealing color types without individually"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "adjusting each color specific region."
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "Users interested in customizing their colors further may adjust"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "the individual color regions, foreground and background, of"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "over fifteen specific characteristics."
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
